title: What's on in Sydney: 20 things to hear, see and do this weekend
text:
The Basics (from left) Kris Schroeder, Tim Heath and Wally De Backer play the Basement on Friday, October 16. 
From the bohemian musical Rent to music with the Basics, a Spring Cycle, two community festivals and Craft Beer Week, we have your weekend more than covered.  
Critics' picks by Elissa Blake, Sharne Wolff, Garry Maddox, Sarah Thomas and Louise Rugendyke. Send entries to  shortlisteditor@smh.com.au
